OL,7,FUTV can reveal senior police officer
OL,8,FJohn Caldwell who narrowly survived a
OL,9,FNew IRA murder bid last year has since
OL,10,Fhad numerous threats to his life.
OL,12,FThe veteran detective, who was shot
OL,13,Fmultiple times outside a sports centre
OL,14,Fin Omagh in front of children
OL,15,Fincluding his own son in February
OL,16,F2023, has had to react quickly to
OL,17,Fwarnings as he goes about his ordinary
OL,18,Fday-to-day life.
