OL,8,Fwas having a quiet drink in a pub in
OL,9,FCo Tyrone and he was told he should
OL,10,Fleave as soon as possible.
OL,12,FSources have told us intelligence came
OL,13,Fin about weapons being moved as it was
OL,14,Fthought dissident knew where the
OL,15,Fdetective was.
OL,17,FOn another occasion ` the chief
OL,18,Finspector was warned of an imminent
OL,19,Fattack ` that he would be shot.
