OL,12,Fconnection with his attempted murder
OL,13,Flast year are in any way linked to
OL,14,Fthis.
OL,16,FFormer senior officer Jon Burrows hit
OL,17,Fout at those behind the threats.
OL,19,F''It's beyond contemptible,'' he said.
