OL,7,F"And it shows how callous and frankly
OL,8,Finhumane these people are.
OL,10,F"John suffered life-changing injuries
OL,11,Fin the attempted murder that he
OL,12,Fendured last year and while he is
OL,13,Ftrying to recover from that physically
OL,14,Fand psychologically, and his family
OL,15,Fand friends are trying to recover from
OL,16,Fthat terrible ordeal, he is being
OL,17,Ftargeted again.
OL,19,F"I think it is simply pure evil and
OL,20,Fabsolutely callous."
