OL,7,FThe PSNI says it does not comment on
OL,8,F''the security of individuals and no
OL,9,Finference should be drawn from this'',
OL,10,Fadding: "However, if we receive
OL,11,Finformation that a person's life may
OL,12,Fbe at risk we will inform them
OL,13,Faccordingly. We never ignore anything
OL,14,Fwhich may put an individual at risk,
OL,15,Fparticularly one of our own colleagues.
OL,17,F"The thoughts of John's friends,
OL,18,Fcolleagues and the entire Service, are
OL,19,Fwith him and his family, as he
OL,20,Fcontinues his recovery journey."
